The following brand-identity assets are **All Rights Reserved** and may not be
reproduced, modified, or distributed without explicit written permission:

- The **"JN" monogram** (`public/favicon.svg`)
- The portrait image (`public/profile-v5.jpg`, `public/profile.jpg`)
- The full **jordannewell.com visual identity** — color palette, dot-grid
  pattern, typography pairing (Inter / Inter Tight / JetBrains Mono) as
